      • findImagebyConcept

        public com.google.common.collect.ListMultimap<java.lang.Double,Image> findImagebyConcept(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Double> conceptList,
                                                                                         ImageCollection iCollection)
        This method allows to search the image collection by querying with a concept
        Parameters:
        conceptList - an hashmap containing the list of concepts for which we want to find relevant images with associated weights. The higher the weight, the more important a concept is in the context of this query and thus the more it will influence retrieval
        iCollection - the collection of images used for retrieval (the same collection that has been indexed). Note that here the collection is used only for metadata information
        Returns:
        the ranking

      • combine

        public com.google.common.collect.ListMultimap<java.lang.Double,Image> combine(com.google.common.collect.ListMultimap<java.lang.Double,Image> a,
                                                                              com.google.common.collect.ListMultimap<java.lang.Double,Image> b,
                                                                              java.lang.Double weight)
        This ancillary method is used to combine two rankings of images
        Parameters:
        a - a ranking of images (with associated scores)
        b - another ranking of images (with associated scores). This is the ranking that needs to be weighted by the weight
        weight - the weight of this concept. Weights multiply the score of a concept for a query
        Returns:
        the merged ranking

      • findImagebyKeyword

        public java.util.List<Image> findImagebyKeyword(java.lang.String akeyword)
        This method allows to search the image collection by querying with a keyword. The retrieved set of images would be those for which the concept description conatined the keyword Note, this method does not support scoring at the moment. TODO: add scoring
        Parameters:
        aKeyword - the query keyword to be used to find relevant images
        Returns:
        a set of images that are relevant to the query keyword
